    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the resource stuff, but is there like a deeper cultural thing? i've heard people say that some of the ethnic groups are just inherently more prone to violence or conflict than others because of their traditional ways of life. in your professional opinion, does the ethnic makeup of a region make it more likely to be unstable?",
